<div class="mt-16 md:mt-0 pb-8">
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 pb-4">
        Looking for a high-quality, beautifully designed home without the hassle of custom construction? Our <b>spec home floorplans</b> offer the perfect solution. <br/>
Our <b>ready-to-build</b> options are crafted for efficiency, style, and comfort. Choose your favorite design, and we’ll build it for you on your land. We also give you the freedom to <b>make your home uniquely yours</b> with options like: <br/>
<ul>
<li>- Flooring styles</li>
<li>- Countertops & cabinetry finishes</li>
<li>- Interior & exterior paint colors</li>
<li>- Siding colors and accents (brick or stone)</li>
<li>- And more, depending on availability!</li>
</ul> <br/>
We’re <b>always adding new designs!</b> If you’re interested in building your dream home with us, or want to know more, <a href="tel:812-243-2759" target="_blank" class="text-[#ffca28] font-bold">call Christa</a> today! <br/>
Your dream home is closer than you think—let’s make it happen!
    </p>
